Item 8.01 Other Events.
On December 21, 2006, Allegiant Air, LLC, a wholly owned operating subsidiary of Allegiant Travel Company (the "Company") took delivery of two MD80 series aircraft under short term lease agreements. The leases provide for an 18 month term. The Company expects to place one leased aircraft into service in December 2006 and one leased aircraft into service in January 2007.
