Item 8.01 Other Events.
On May 11, 2007, Allegiant Air, LLC, a wholly owned operating subsidiary of Allegiant Travel Company (the "Company") took delivery of one MD80 series aircraft under an operating lease agreement with a fixed price purchase option. The lease provides for a 66 month term, with the purchase option becoming effective in 42 months. The Company expects to place this aircraft into service in June 2007. This will be the Companys 28th aircraft.
Top of the Form
