Item 8.01 Other Events.
Allegiant Travel Company (the "Company") estimates that its average fuel price per gallon for February 2008 will be approximately $2.74 per gallon. This estimated price per gallon includes the cost of aircraft fuel, fuel taxes, into plane fees and airport fuel flowage, storage and through-put fees, net of fuel cost reimbursements under certain of our fixed fee flying agreements. Under the safe harbor provisions of the Private Securities Litigation Reform Act of 1995, information contained in this Item 8.01 that does not constitute historical facts, including those statements that refer to the Companys February 2008 estimates, are forward-looking statements. These forward-looking statements are not historical facts, but are only current estimates or predictions. The Company does not undertake any obligation to update any of the forward-looking statements after the date of this Form 8-K.
