Allegiant Air, LLC, a subsidiary of Allegiant Travel Company, has received notification from the National Mediation Board (NMB) that it has authorized a representation election for Allegiant Air pilots. The International Brotherhood of Teamsters, Airline Division filed the application for a representation election on behalf of Allegiant Air pilots. The voting period will be from August 2, 2012, through August 23, 2012. The election result tally will take place on August 23, 2012 at 2:00 p.m., Eastern Time.
 
 
 
 
